headline: TransDigm's Q1 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Sales Increase Y/Y
summary: TDG beats Q1 earnings and sales estimates as revenues jump 14%. It also raises its fiscal 2026 sales and adjusted EPS guidance.

headline: Woodward's Q1 Earnings & Revenues Beat Estimates, Up Y/Y, Stock Rises
summary: WWD posts a Q1 FY26 EPS beat and 29% sales growth and lifts full-year outlook. Shares jump 15% after strong Aerospace and Industrial demand.
